{"id":"straw","term":"Straw","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Used in brick-making (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 5:7\">Ex. 5:7-18</a>). Used figuratively in <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Job 41:27\">Job 41:27</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 11:7\">Isa. 11:7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 25:10\">25:10</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 65:25\">65:25</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Exodus 5:7","Job 41:27","Isaiah 11:7","Isaiah 25:10","Isaiah 65:25"]}